## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
# 1. Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/priyanshii56/ecommerce-sales-eda.git
cd ecommerce-sales-eda

# 2. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 3. Download dataset
# Go to: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/carrie1/ecommerce-data
# Download data.csv and place it in the project folder

# 4. Launch notebook
jupyter notebook notebook.ipynb
```

---

## 📁 Dataset
- **Source:** [UCI E-Commerce Data — Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/carrie1/ecommerce-data)
- **Records:** ~541,000 transactions
- **Period:** Dec 2010 – Dec 2011
- **Region:** UK-based online retail store

